Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.54,0:00:11.69,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}I want to shine on you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.96,0:00:15.03,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}And always light the dazzling sun
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.33,0:00:18.52,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}I want to defend you from all the darkness
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.85,0:00:23.39,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}This is the truth from my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.61,0:00:34.83,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}心の奥 系げたら 信じてもらえるのにね
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.05,0:00:46.13,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}今见えなくても 失くさないでいて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.51,0:00:54.21,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}その优しさは无驮じゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.92,0:00:58.33,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}风に乘って浮かび
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.60,0:01:01.67,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}ここじゃないどこかへ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.00,0:01:05.19,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}海を越え　时を越え
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.47,0:01:08.73,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}きっと咲くだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.98,0:01:15.39,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}いつの日にも　いつもそんな君を
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.77,0:01:22.34,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}太阳のようにずっと见守れたらいいな
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.75,0:01:30.33,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}This is truth From my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.20,0:00:00.20,ed_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}ひざ抱え一人泪こらえた
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.20,0:00:00.20,ed_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}どうしようもない 不安に负けそうな夜
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.20,0:00:00.20,ed_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}气がつけばいつだってすぐそばに
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.20,0:00:00.20,ed_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}ほかの谁でも 泣くあなたがいてくれた
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.20,0:00:00.20,ed_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}强くなりたい
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.20,0:00:00.20,ed_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}愿い续けてはまたつまづいて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.20,0:00:00.20,ed_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}气づつくけど信じられるあなたがいるから
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.20,0:00:00.20,ed_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}立ち上がれるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.20,0:00:00.20,ed_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}ありがとう
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.20,0:00:00.20,ed_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}ただ伝えたい爱しい人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.20,0:00:00.20,ed_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}声の限り何度だって
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.20,0:00:00.20,ed_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}かけがえのない私の爱しい人へ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.20,0:00:00.20,ed_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}届いていますか
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.20,0:00:00.20,ed_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}变わり行く世界　变わらない人の温もり
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.20,0:00:00.20,ed_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}确かに感じた
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.20,0:00:00.20,ed_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}爱しい人
